        "description": {
            "value": "<p>When a creature enters this snare's square, it triggers an extremely loud clockwork device, which explodes with a bang that can be heard from 200 feet away and deals [[/r {1d8}[fire]]]{1d8 fire damage}. The creature must attempt a <span data-pf2-check=\"reflex\" data-pf2-dc=\"18\" data-pf2-traits=\"clockwork,fire,mechanical,snare,trap\" data-pf2-label=\"Noisemaker Snare DC\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"gm\">Reflex</span> save.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The creature is unaffected.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The creature takes half damage.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The creature takes full damage and is @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Deafened]{Deafened} for 1 round.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The creature takes double damage and is @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Deafened]{Deafened} for 1 minute.</p>"
